    {
      "assets": [],
      "author": "yanqingwang",
      "description": "## 🔧 Fixes\n\nResolved all warnings from the Obsidian automated review scan:\n\n- **no-unsafe-assignment**: `parseYaml()` and `loadData()` return values now properly typed\n- **no-unsafe-call / no-unsafe-member-access**: Regex callback params explicitly typed\n- **unnecessary assertion**: Removed redundant `as string` and `as HEHTMLView` casts (instanceof already narrows)\n- **unnecessary escape**: Removed \\\\/ escape in template literal\n- **activeDocument**: Use `container.ownerDocument` instead of global `document`\n- **builtin-modules**: Pre-existing dev dependency warning (non-blocking)\n\n### Zoom feature from v1.0.17 unchanged:\n- Ctrl+wheel / Ctrl+=/-/0 zoom in HTML viewer\n- Floating zoom bar with +/−/reset\n- localStorage persistence\n- Auto-skip for files with existing zoom controls",
      "downloadCount": 0,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "v1.0.18 — Fix lint warnings flagged by Obsidian review",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-07-11T02:01:03Z",
      "tag": "v1.0.18"
    },
    {
      "assets": [],
      "author": "yanqingwang",
      "description": "## ✨ What's New\n\n### Zoom Controls in HTML Viewer\nWhen opening .html files in Obsidian, you can now zoom in/out:\n\n- **Zoom bar**: floating bottom-right bar with +/−/reset buttons (auto-hides until hover)\n- **Ctrl+wheel**: scroll to zoom\n- **Ctrl+= / Ctrl+- / Ctrl+0**: keyboard shortcuts\n- **Persistence**: zoom level saved to localStorage, remembers across sessions\n- **Auto-skip**: files already containing zoom controls (e.g. html-effectiveness generated) are left untouched\n\n### Fixes\n- Fixed TypeScript error: `isDead()` removed in favor of null check on leaf.view",
      "downloadCount": 0,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "v1.0.17 — Zoom controls in HTML viewer",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-07-11T01:21:37Z",
